Package com.esplibrary.data

Class AlertData

java.lang.Object
com.esplibrary.data.AlertData
public class AlertData extends Object
Created by JDavis on 3/16/2016. AlertData represents alerts being displayed on the Valentine One front display, with additional data. The additional data includes: Total number of alerts the Alert table that 'this' alert belongs, index in the Alert table of 'this' alert, the band, frequency, and direction of 'this' alert, as well as if it is the priority alert.
